    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>召唤你的最强阵容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场战斗，都从你的召唤开始。它们是你策略的核心，也是胜利的关键。每个召唤都有独特定位：有的冲锋陷阵，有的坚守防线，还有的在登场瞬间爆发毁灭性力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤物会自主战斗，而你出牌的时机与位置，将决定整个局势。操作节奏、部署配合、团队协调每一步都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的召唤，让策略鲜活起来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/660cc8ad0884b8ade21a13e1dd9a9dd8.poster.avif?t=1762991810\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/660cc8ad0884b8ade21a13e1dd9a9dd8.webm?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/660cc8ad0884b8ade21a13e1dd9a9dd8.mp4?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构筑你的卡组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡组就是你的战术蓝图。打造由十张召唤卡与三张 Wildcards 组成的活力武库，定义你的战斗风格。每一张卡牌都蕴含可能性：稳固防线的坦克、直冲核心的突击手、扰乱敌阵的诡计者，还有能强化全队的 Wildcards。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜利不仅取决于操作，更取决于灵活的构筑。平衡进攻与防守，与队友的配置相互呼应，让你的战术在每一场对局中不断进化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的卡组，就是你的身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/55c7bde751c27c872de02aea79201251.poster.avif?t=1762991810\" width=1170 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/55c7bde751c27c872de02aea79201251.webm?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/55c7bde751c27c872de02aea79201251.mp4?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的冠军</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的冠军是你在竞技场中的化身，让你的策略真正落地。每位冠军都拥有独特技能，与召唤物形成绝妙配合。而在 Wildcard 中，<strong>团队协作才是一切的核心。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜利来自你对时机的把握 让冠军的技能与召唤的推进、队友的节奏完美同步。支援进攻、掩护突破、抓住瞬间出击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顶级冠军，永远打得心有灵犀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/e71388176ba8def1f2490386b8b4edcb.poster.avif?t=1762991810\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/e71388176ba8def1f2490386b8b4edcb.webm?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/e71388176ba8def1f2490386b8b4edcb.mp4?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>征战史诗竞技场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入专为高强度 2v2 对战打造的竞技场！每张地图都有独特地形与挑战 视野、坡度、掩体与战术点位，等待你与队友灵活利用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的搭档协同召唤、连招与走位，突破防线、击败守门者、打碎护盾、夺取核心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次完美的操作，都是迈向胜利的一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/fd3cbe15919e3887c37ca40d1432c1ab.poster.avif?t=1762991810\" width=1170 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/fd3cbe15919e3887c37ca40d1432c1ab.webm?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/fd3cbe15919e3887c37ca40d1432c1ab.mp4?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进入竞技场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舞台已备，卡组待命，队伍就绪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否带领召唤军团夺得荣耀，驾驭冠军的全部潜能？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >答案，只有踏入竞技场才能揭晓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>勇者无畏，荣耀加身。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/6a068a0de18258fba2623a4984108f33.poster.avif?t=1762991810\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/6a068a0de18258fba2623a4984108f33.webm?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497120/extras/6a068a0de18258fba2623a4984108f33.mp4?t=1762991810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
